  "instructions": [
    "Combine nduja, pasta water, capers, chopped dill, toasted breadcrumbs, chopped prosciutto, grated ginger, low-sodium soy sauce, apple cider vinegar, crushed red pepper flakes, black pepper, and garlic powder in a bowl to make the nduja mixture. ",
    "Heat a robata grill to 450F. ",
    "Grill 10 minutes per side or to your desired level of doneness for the wagyu beef cubes. ",
    "Transfer grilled wagyu beef cubes to the robata grill and brush with black truffle oil. ",
    "Serve with the nduja mixture and topped with crumbled feta cheese and chopped fresh parsley. ",
